Whether you’re looking for inspiration, step-by-step tutorials, or a little motivation to start your next project, we’ve got you covered. Let’s build, create, and transform together!

snippet.title: DIYで理想のお家づくり
snippet.description:
可愛いお家に憧れて、20年位セルフリノベで空間作りをしています。
(アメブロ歴は10年)
自宅の他にも実家所有のアパートのリノベや、お洒落な空間にして貸し出す戸建て賃貸も始めました。

現在は築40年の中古戸建を自分たちで住む為に購入し、一棟まるごとセルフリノベをしています。
現在進行形のセルフリノベの様子を中心に過去のリノベも紹介していきます。

なるべくお金をかけずに、でも拘る所は拘ってDIYならではの空間づくりで理想のお家を目指します。

ヤギさんに囲まれて生活してます。
将来オフグリッド生活で自分らしく暮らして行く。
そんな想いから耕作放棄地に基地を作りながら、トラックに乗せて移動も可能な住居、モバイルハウスを制作中。

snippet.title: DIY With Z
snippet.description:
Welcome to my YouTube channel where I bring remote control models! From cars and trucks to boats, tractors, trolleys, and even science projects, I love to build and tinker with them all.

Using DC motors and transmitter and receiver, I create fully functional and realistic models that you can control from a distance. Whether you're a fan of construction machinery, or cars or love the sight of an RC truck, there's something for everyone here.

My videos showcase the step-by-step process of building each model, including all the details on how I select the materials, and how I reuse and recycle the materials. I also love to experiment with new ideas, so you'll see plenty of science projects and other unique creations here as well.

So if you're a fan of remote control models, or love to see how things work, be sure to subscribe to my channel and join me on this exciting journey of building and to explore!

snippet.title: Chic & easy DIY
snippet.description:
Hi everyone, glad to see you on my channel! My name is Lesya, I live in Ukraine 💙💛. I love to come up with ideas for crafts DIY 💖 On this channel you will find a lot of creative ideas for creativity. Every week I will upload videos with crafts from various affordable and simple materials and even from garbage😁 I love turning garbage into stylish home decor. I will create detailed master classes for you in different techniques. You can see how to make stylish home decor DIY, create unusual decorations, gifts for friends, toys for the Christmas tree and the Christmas tree itself. Together we will remake old clothes and shoes, sew exclusive bags with our own hands and many other interesting things, join us 🥰👌
I invite you to engage in relaxing creativity, to create beauty from everything that is at hand. Surprise your friends and loved ones with your crafts and souvenirs. Come to my channel, share your opinion in the comments and subscribe. I will be very glad to everyone💖😊

snippet.title: じぶん流DIYちゃんねる
snippet.description:
自己紹介はライフハッカー様より取材していただいた記事を
リンクからご覧いただけると幸いです。
DIYを始めたきっかけや思いなどをお話させていただいております。

都内から90分程度のプチ田舎の鹿嶋市に、土地100坪の平屋を１５０万で購入。
DIYでリノベーションを施して定年後の住まいにしようと考えています。
将来の夢は「リタイヤ盲導犬の引き取りボランティア」
ドックラン付きの素敵な平屋を目指して奮闘する日々をご覧ください。
一般会社員のためDIY作業は休日しか出来ません。よって、新作配信は月に2回程度が限度です。
コツコツとDIY並びに配信を頑張りますので、お付き合いをお願いいたします。

Welcome to the DIY Boomers channel! We’re here to inspire and inform you for your related DIY Projects.

YouTube continues to grow into a great resource for information on just about any topic. Having benefited from this information, we thought that we would share our DIY experiences with others so that they would be better prepared to tackle projects that they might otherwise be hesitant to try. We aim to combine quality products that make projects easiest to complete, while staying reasonable with the expense.

Our initial projects include a John Deere S130 playlist, and a Bathroom Remodel playlist with rerouting plumbing, to bathroom floor and shower tiling, to installing all the bathroom finishes. Being Boomers ourselves, we show that DIYers at any age can tackle DIY projects.

We hope that you find the content useful and enjoy the videos, If you do, please hit the subscribe button and leave us some comments. Thanks for watching!

snippet.description:
DIY projects ; Woodworking & More …

Welcome to REMEDIAL DIY. My Name is Ndivhuwo Nelwamondo; I am a Wife, Mother &  an Academic, and Being a mom is one of my most significant accomplishments.
 
Making furniture and anything DIY is rewarding and therapeutic for me,  When I make a video, I want you to be a part of it, so I show you all of the steps to join this fantastic journey. Weekly I will upload Easy DIY videos to make cool affordable things for your home. You will learn to make your alternatives to store-bought accessories, furniture, and other DIY projects.

#DIYBYNdivhuwo  #REMEDIALDIY #NdivhuwoNelwamondo

The Type of videos  :  
-Furniture DIY
 - DIY Furniture and home decor.
 - Woodworking and Essential Wood projects. 
-Woodworking tutorials for beginners and many more.


Thank you, and please join me in this journey

Johannes Brahms

בס"ד

ברוכים הבאים לסימפל טאץ' עשה זאת בעצמך Simple Touch DIY
הערוץ מיועד לאנשי מקצוע וחובבנים כאחד המעוניינים לקבל כלים ועזרה במלאכות שונות. בערוץ זה תוכלו ליהנות מתכנים רבים שיעזרו לכם לעשות זאת בעצמכם.
צפייה מהנה!

מוזמנים להצטרף לערוץ הוואטסאפ ולקבל שם סרטונים באונליין לפני כולם מבלי הצורך בכניסה לערוץ היוטיוב וקבלת לינקים לכלי העבודה שבכל סרטון. הערוץ הוא שקט ללא כל הודעות של מנויי הערוץ.

גילוי נאות:
הערוץ נתמך ע"י שיווק שותפים (affiliate marketing), ובחלק מהסרטונים יופיע לינק שותף בתיאור הסרטון ו/או בתגובות לסרטון.

Welcome to Simple Touch DIY
The channel is intended for professionals and amateurs alike who are interested in receiving tools and help in various crafts. In this channel you will enjoy many content that will help you do it yourself.
pleasant viewing!

snippet.title: 【DIYニキ】Tom |家族で日本一周
snippet.description:
＼中古のハイエースをDIYして子連れ日本一周／

初めまして！
家族で日本一周している
ANCHOR WORKS（アンカーワークス）です。

Tom、Kahoさん、ニャンちゃん、チーくん！

私たちは４３００万円の新築を3年で売却して新たな住居を探すために
家族で日本一周しています。
夫→元電車の運転士
妻→元看護師
安定を求めて働いていたものの仕事に追われる日々。
このままの人生でいいのか、人生は一度きりだと思い
新築の家、仕事を手放し日本一周することにしました。
小さい子供を連れての旅は大変。
子供がいるから出来ないと言い訳もしたくない・・・
やってみないと何事も分からない。
そんな私たちは旅に出た、

DIYでハイエースを外装から内装全て仕上げました。

TomはDIYerで内装から外構、家具、キャンプギアまで
なんでも作っています。（クセ強）

＜これから＞
家族で日本一周→空き家を探す→DIYで空き家をリノベ→〇〇


子供がいても旅が出来る、子連れバンライフのリアルをお届けします。

フォローよろしくお願いします。


📱SNS
Instagram

Tom : https://www.instagram.com/anchorworks.jp/ 


妻（かーさん）：https://www.instagram.com/kahoma_n/


TikTok：　https://www.tiktok.com/@anchorworks..jp







Amazonのアソシエイトとして、当メディアは適格販売により収入を得ています。

snippet.title: The DIY Grunt
snippet.description:
Welcome to The DIY Grunt, I’m Nikko!

I was introduced to DIY as a kid, helping my parents remodel our entire house. Growing up as a military brat, this process happened several times. I love the feeling of pride and accomplishment in creating and fixing things without having to hire a professional. 

In 2014, I joined the military and served as an Infantryman (affectionately known as a Grunt). After several deployments, I decided it was time to move on and focus on my passion for DIY home and car projects.

I am also a fan of classic Porsches and currently own three of them. I look forward to doing a video series on rebuilding and modifying each of them in the future.

*Disclaimer: I am strictly a DIYer. I am NOT a trained/certified professional. Everything on my channel is based on my own experiences and research. If you feel uncomfortable with a project, please seek a professional in your area for further assistance.

I am also a fan of classic Porsches and currently own three of them. I look forward to doing a video series on rebuilding and modifying each of them in the future.

*Disclaimer: I am strictly a DIYer. I am NOT a trained/certified professional. Everything on my channel is based on my own experiences and research. If you feel uncomfortable with a project, please seek a professional in your area for further assistance.

snippet.title: The DIY Cabin Guy
snippet.description:
Are you dreaming of a more flexible and fulfilling lifestyle? So was I which led me to start building my financial freedom from the ground up as I am building a Cabin by myself which I will rent on Airbnb as a short term rental. 

My name is Tristan! I have no prior building experience but decided I would build a Cabin anyway (Tiny house) and document every step of my journey. I am showing you everything from foundation, framing, roofing, electrical, plumbing, heating and cooling...etc. This is going to be an epic journey so make sure to subscribe as I take on this major challenge!
Once the cabin is built, I plan on renting it out and will show you all the aspects of short term rentals (Airbnb, VRBO) and share all the numbers associated with the building process, income and expenses.

I will post a new video every two weeks. You can also join my emailing list at TheDIYCabinGuy.com/blueprint

For any business inquiry, or to just say Hi , you can email me at thediycabinguy@gmail.com.

snippet.title: Maxi Size DIY
snippet.description:
Maxi Size DIY – канал для пышных женщин. 
Которых не устраивает имеющаяся в продаже женская одежда. 
Которые ищут элегантные практичные решения, КАК УВЕЛИЧИТЬ ОДЕЖДУ, как сделать РЕМОНТ ОДЕЖДЫ, чтобы она хорошо выглядела и сидела. 
Которые предпочитают свои наряды ШИТЬ САМОЙ.

В магазинах продаётся одежда больших размеров мрачная, не модная и не дешёвая. Будто стильная ОДЕЖДА ДЛЯ ПОЛНЫХ ЖЕНЩИН, ЖЕНСКАЯ ОДЕЖДА БОЛЬШИХ РАЗМЕРОВ на фабриках не шьётся. Выход – ОДЕЖДА СВОИМИ РУКАМИ. Но пошив одежды из новых тканей влетает в копеечку.

Меня выручает ОДЕЖДА ИЗ СЕКОНД ХЕНДА. Я могу купить дешёвые красивые вещи и сшить комбинированные изделия. ПЕРЕДЕЛКА ОДЕЖДЫ – решение всех проблем: копеечная стоимость, качественные материалы, подходящий размер, приятные расцветки, идеальные фасоны. 

Я показываю, как делаю перешив одежды, делюсь идеями, доказываю, что королевский гардероб при минимальном бюджете возможен. 
Заходите, смотрите, подписывайтесь! Будет интересно!
Кстати, меня зовут Лариса )))

snippet.title: DIY Cosmetica
snippet.description:
This channel was created to inspire and motivate you to do your own skincare products.
The videos are meant to give you some ideas and a rough guide to make cosmetics. However, this is not a formulation course nor an educative channel. If you wish to become a formulator, you should consider a formulation course.
If you wish to sell your products, you always have to check the regulations at your country/region and obtain the necessary certification required. 
You should always ask your doctor before using or applying any ingredient.
Also take into consideration that some ingredients can not be used if you are pregnant or breast feeding.

snippet.title: Medicated Housewife DIY's
snippet.description: I'm The Medicated Housewife™ and this is my DIY Channel.  My name is Sayre and I've been "crafting" all my life.  Like so many people, I've battled depression and anxiety for many years, and crafting has been an incredible stress reliever for me.  I'm hoping to share my creativity and enthusiasm with others.  I've been making Dollar Tree (and other "sourced") projects for Home Decor for years, and nothing makes me happier than figuring out a way to create my own version of the things I see, but for less and with my own personal twist.  My personal style is all over the map, and I think there should be no labels when it comes to your personal style.  If it looks good to you....then it's good. I hope you enjoy watching and would love to hear from you about things you'd like to see me create in the future.  I'm the Medicated Housewife™, and crafting is my medication. 😃  New Videos weekly.

snippet.title: Debt-Free DIY
snippet.description: Hi, we're Jeremy and Jess! In 2016 we sold our completely finished home and bought a fixer upper. About a year later, we decided to stop everything and pay off all of our consumer debt before beginning all the renovations on our list. In 15 months we paid off $34,000 dollars in debt and then began putting back for our emergency fund. Now we're punching our remodel in the face and using cash instead of debt. Follow along as we go room by room through our home tackling everything from DIY to design all without borrowing a penny!

snippet.title: DIY Japan
snippet.description:
My name is Danny. Join me as I attempt to renovate an old abandoned house, known as akiya, in Japan. The house is located in the rural serene countryside ( inaka ) coastal town called Ine in Kyoto prefecture. This is my attempt to restart my life in a way I intended to live it since I was younger. I have always enjoyed a slower pace of life and realized that I have spent half my life in busy cities and never realized my dream to live somewhere peaceful and without the hustle and stress of big cities.

I left Osaka city (escaped) and now I will attempt to make a living in the Japanese countryside and renovated the cheap house I bought. I will do most of the work myself and try to share everything I learned along the way. I will also share about local culture, Japanese stories, and humor along the way to make the videos not only informative but fun. Let's enjoy the adventure together!

snippet.title: DIY mit Elisa
snippet.description:
Hallo liebe Freunde meines Kanals, mein Name ist Elisa und ich möchte Euch gerne kurz erzählen, was Ihr auf meinem Kanal erwarten dürft. :) Ich poste regelmäßig Videos rund um das Thema Handarbeit. Jede Woche Freitag um 19 Uhr lade ich eine neue Folge meines Strickpodcasts hoch, in dem ich euch meine fertigen Werke und meine Projekte vorstelle. Außerdem lasse ich euch in diesem Podcast an meinem Alltag teilhaben. 
Oft lade ich auch Anleitungen hoch, die euch zeigen, wie ihr zB. ein Strickmuster, eine gestrickte Socke, eine genähte Decke oder Ähnliches fertigt. 


Ihr wollt mir eure Strickwerke zeigen, die ihr nach meiner Anleitung gestrickt habt? Ihr habt Fragen oder Wünsche für Videos? Dann schreibt mir eine Email, in der ihr mir zeigt, was ihr gestrickt oder gebastelt habt. Über Fragen oder Videowünsche freue ich mich auch sehr. Meine Email lautet: diymitelisa@gmx.de

snippet.title: Field Guide to DIY
snippet.description:
Helping you SAVE TIME and MONEY by showing how to DO IT YOURSELF!!!

My name is Eddie Field.  I am a Christ-follower.  I enjoy bad dad jokes and saving money.  You might even call me a cheapskate.  I learned so much from my dad and have had so many of my friends ask how I fixed this or built that.  So I decided you might want to know.

We feature how-tos, projects, product reviews, tips, tricks, and hacks.  We talk about woodworking, electrical, plumbing and all-around home improvement for folks on a budget or just wanting to know how.

Field Guide to DIY is designed to help you do just that -- DO IT YOURSELF!

Please let me know if you have any questions or comments.  Thanks for checking the channel out.

snippet.title: DIY LIFE
snippet.description:
こんにちは DIY LIFEと申します。

この動画は誰でも業者に頼んだようなクオリティに！というのをテーマに
福岡市の住宅地に築37年3LDK中古マンションを購入。

よくある新築35年ローンなどでの住宅購入は一切考えておらず、比較的に安値で購入できました。
素人の夫婦がちからを合わせて なるべくお金を掛けず業者にリフォームを依頼したようなクオリティを目指して行きます。

部屋全体のテーマはおしゃれで湿度調整に優れた漆喰を使い、南プロヴァンス風に仕上げて行きたいと考えています。

snippet.title: DIY Tinkerer
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel.

I’m a retired six sigma IT consultant, but don’t let that put you off, my family never understood what I did for a living so I don’t expect you to either - and I promise to not mention it again!

Like many people at working age my interests took a back seat and now I’m retired I’m free to explore them and learn the skills needed to be successful at them. This channel is about my journey and I’d love you to share it with me, either as a sage I can listen to and learn from through the comments or someone not so far along the road that I can pass what I’ve learnt onto.

I’m not sure how it will turn out but you are welcome to find out with me.

皆さんと一緒に成長できたらと思っています！
やる気だけは人一倍あります！

Your friend,
Sarah with Jujubee DIY

Desejo tudo de melhor pra você!

snippet.title: ムーさんちのDIY【余白のある暮らし】
snippet.description:
ムーさんちのＤＩＹをご覧いただきありがとうございます♪

【好きなコトやモノを大切に、人生を充実させるためのシンプルな空間づくり】をするべく２０２０年１月に子供部屋からスタート♪人生折り返し地点をあと数年で迎えるにあたって、ＤＩＹをしながらモノを整理しよう！って決めました。そして何より、明日が少しでも良くなるように、｢今日は何をしようかな～？？｣って毎日思うのです。

ＤＩＹを初めて、早２４年。モノづくりの好きな夫と、アイデアを考えるコトが好きな妻。→動きがフリーズしているときは必ず何かをたくらんでいます。（笑）ハハハ

今の住まいではありませんが、一番最初に作ったのは確か・・・下駄箱。ＤＩＹ初心者なのに大物に手を出してしまいましたが、(￣｡￣;)ＤＩＹのおかげでサイズもピッタリ『こんなのあったらいいな～』が叶った瞬間でした。

振り返ると小さいモノから大きいモノまで、たくさんのＤＩＹをしてきました！！インテリア雑貨も好きだったので、雑貨巡りでいろいろ集めてモノが増え、いつしかそれを置くための棚やシェルフまでがあちこちに。これからは収納もモノもコンパクトにして身軽にしていこうと思っています。

なので・・・これからは
①時短になるコト
②掃除が楽なコト
③片付けがしやすいコト
この3つのコトをなるべく意識しながらＤＩＹをしていこうと思ってます。

最後に・・・
二人はそれぞれ仕事をしながら、休みの日にＤＩＹ＋撮影＋編集をしていますので配信日がなかなか決められませんが、少しずつ変わっていく様子を一緒に楽しんで見て頂ければ幸いです。そして少しでも参考になれば、嬉しいです♪


【お問い合わせはこちら】
musan.diy.official@gmail.com

♦︎只今 Instagram準備中です♦︎

Этот канал о том, как при желании и вдохновении можно создать красивое пространство вокруг себя. 

Перед Новым годом 2018 я, вместе со своей семьёй, переехала загород в частный дом. Так ремонт и всё что с ним связано - плотно вошли в мою жизнь. 

Мне вдруг захотелось переделать кресло, сделать шкаф своими руками, смастерить ящики, создать новогодний декор и много чего ещё безумно интересного. А потом я подумала, что будет здорово делиться этим, ведь мои видео могут оказаться полезными или вдохновить кого-то на переделку пространства вокруг себя. Так появился этот канал. На этом канале вы найдете видео о ремонте, создании мебели своими руками и простые МК по декору и не только!

Так что да, я Маша и тут я всё делаю своими руками.

snippet.title: DIY avec POLO
snippet.description:
Je m'appelle Paul : artisan du bâtiment depuis plus de 17 ans et je suis toujours autant passionné par mon métier ! 
J'ai la chance d'avoir un quotidien très varié du fait de mon activité généraliste : la rénovation !

J'aime partager ma passion et c'est pour cette raison que sur cette chaine vous trouverez beaucoup de conseils en bâtiment, en investissement , des tutos de mises en œuvre, des astuces de bricolage, de la mécanique, et parfois même juste des coups de cœur que j'aime partager !

snippet.title: DIY - Tota
snippet.description:
من أنا ؟ 
اسمى يوسى  من مصر  

ماذا درست ؟
حصلت على بكالريوس تربية رياض اطفال بتقدير عام جيد جدا  ودبلومة مهنية قسم زوى الاحتياجات الخاصة بتقدير عام جيد 

بماذا اهتم وماذا احب ؟
احب الاعمال اليدوية بصفة عامة وايضا اعشق فن الكروشية 

ما الذى اقدمة فى قناتى ؟
قناة DIY - Tota    
قناة هى قناة عربية مصرية لتعلم الاشغال والأعمال اليدوية البسيطة وغير المكلفة والافكار المتنوعة والجديدة والتجارب المختلفة بخامات متوافرة فى كل بيت /و هى عالمى الخاص التى ابذل فيها الكثير من الوقت والجهد لتقديم كل ماهو جديد فى هذا المجال وافادة الجميع 
 
هل لديك قناة اخرى على اليوتيوب ؟
نعم   قناة yoyo crochet  لتعليم فن الكروشية خطوة بخطوة 
لينك القناة https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7_hUO1VOD2_seNfkKMfbrw/featured?disable_polymer=1

# قناتى هى عالمى الخاص التى أبذل فيها الكثير من الوقت والجهد لتقديم كل ماهو جديد فى هذا المجال 
# ارجو الاشتراك بالقناة والضغط على علامة الجرس ليصلك اشعار بكل جديد 
# وسأكون سعيدة بتعليقك على الفيديو فكل التعليقات مرحب بها وموضع اهتمام كبير

snippet.title: Life & DIY
snippet.description:
I'm Holly - on this channel you'll find videos about health, life, longevity, skincare, supplements, biohacking & other experiments where I take you along for the journey and share results with you. I am infinitely curious & passionate about discovering what works and what doesn't, while sharing unique and interesting resources with you along the way. 

My passion for health is personal & began because of life-altering injuries my son & I had over a decade ago. My goal is to continually improve my health as I age, always experimenting, with a DIY approach. I know you're on your own journey, and I hope you'll join me here, as we have a wonderful & supportive community.

I live in the woods near the UP & I love it because it's rustic, with lots of wildlife. My work & other passion is online marketing & I've been doing it since 2005, at home. I'm an Army Veteran, where I served as a Journalist. I traveled a lot years ago, living all over, but I am now content with life in the woods.

snippet.title: DIYと猫Lifeおじさん
snippet.description:
離婚して寂しいので
100円DIYを始めました。
7カ月後、寂しさのあまり保護猫6歳(茶々さん)
のトライアルに挑戦します。
これは、30代オジサンの成長日記です。
YouTubeやInstagramでUPしていきます。

Hello, I’m ¥100 and I’m from Japan.
I know this is sudden but I had a divorce. Afterwards I was
very lonely.
So! I adopted a rescue cat from an Adoptive Cat Cafe.
Her name is Chacha-san and she’s 6 years old.
She used to live with an old lady but due to financial
problems she was given to the Cat Cafe. It’s been 6 months
since I’ve adopted her.
I’m very happy to have the chance to share our life
together as well as useful DIY projects for people overseas.

snippet.title: バリカタさんのDIYキャンプ工房
snippet.description:
素人作業ですが、『創って、作って、使う』をモットーにキャンプギアを中心としたDIY方法、アイディアを共有しています。
主に、ホームセンター，100均ダイソー，セリア，インテリア系製造物流小売のニトリ・イケア・無印良品の素材を活用して、焚き火台やラック、テーブルなどのキャンプ道具を自作しています。

DIYの情報発信が、キャンプグッズを作る楽しみ、自作した品への愛着に繋がり、アウトドアライフのさらなる充実と満足度向上に貢献し、多くの方々のココロとカラダの健康促進に寄与出来れば幸いです。

DIYすることに幸せ、充実感を感じておられる皆さま、人とはちょっと違うソロキャンプをお楽しみの皆さま、これからキャンプを始められる皆さま、互いに創意工夫して、手軽なアウトドアライフを是非一緒にエンジョイしましょう！

●歴
学生時代からスピーカーの大型エンクロージャ、オーディオラックの自作を繰り返し、社会人になってから2階を好き勝手にリフォームして楽しむ。
1993年、第一次オートキャンプブームに乗っかりグループ・ファミリーキャンプにハマり、テーブル、キッチンラックなどを自作して楽しむ。
転勤につぐ転勤に伴い、「車中泊」「完組みの自転車ツーリング泊」「南北アルプステント泊登山」「ソロキャンプ」と変化。
2019年9月、バリカタさんのDIYキャンプ工房　としてリビング，青空工房での作業風景の共有を開始。

●NEWS
・レコメンドサイト「イチオシ」（All About × NTT docomo）で「イチオシスト」に認定（2021年2月）、SmartNewsにも掲載

●メディア掲載
・キャンプ好き愛用の明かりギアコンテストで、自作した木工ランタンが最優秀作品賞を受賞。BE-PAL 2020年9月号掲載
・イチオシ100均アイテムコンテストで、カスタマイズした木製握り手トングが最優秀作品賞を受賞。BE-PAL 2021年6月号掲載
・DIYを特集したBE-PAL 2022年3月号にスパイスボックス，オイルランタン掲載

NHK ドキュメント72時間の取材を受けた涸沢のキャンプ場が一番好きです。クタクタになって着いたばかりの他愛のない会話の取材で見事に没になってトレックライズ0のみ登場しましたけど。ほとんど星の中の点でした（笑）

Twitter　:　　@DIY_Balikata

snippet.title: GMS JATENG & DIY
snippet.description:
GMS adalah gereja sel yang apostolik dan profetik. Gereja yang dipenuhi oleh rupa-rupa karunia Roh Kudus dan bergerak dalam Amanat Agung untuk menjadikan semua bangsa murid Kristus. GMS dibawah penggembalaan Ps. Philip Mantofa kini telah berkembang menjadi gereja yang bertumbuh cepat ke arah 100.000 jemaat dalam gereja-gereja lokal yang tersebar di seluruh negeri, bahkan sampai ke Asia, Australia, Eropa & Amerika

Untuk layanan jemaat: 
- Menerima Tuhan Yesus
- Baptisan
- Bergabung dalam Connect Group- Komunitas Kecil
- Kesaksian
- Permohonan doa & konseling
dapat dikirimkan ke https://gms.church/connect. 

Untuk Persembahan & Persepuluhan Jemaat GMS Church, dapat diberikan melalui https://gms.church/give

snippet.title: LOFT DIY
snippet.description:
Всем привет. Меня зовут Константин. 
Данный канал посвящён строительной и дачной тематике. 

Купили как-то мои друзья дачу. Года 3 туда никто не ездил. Потом решили сделать беседку и ездить туда откушивать шашлыки. И понеслось... Решили построить дом после беседки. Опыта в стройке не было от слова совсем. Решил я углубиться в вопрос строительства, изучить каркасную технологию, проектирование. Ничего сложного - примерно полгода почти ежедневного изучения по несколько часов в день, разработка проекта месяца три и готово) Разработал проект, документацию, построили прикольный дом, ка по мне. Все этапы строительства выкладывал на канале. Разжился собственным участком, там построил большую мастерскую, имеется много интересных мыслей по столярке и металлообработке. Лежит душа к этим вопросам, так сказать. В 2022 на этом участке планирую начинать строить дом для себя. 

Сотрудничество:
Почта:  loft4diy@gmail.com
https://vk.com/loft_diy
https://instagram.com/loft_diy

snippet.title: Liyana DIY
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel!
I love DIY's, decor & crafting, and I share my love for creativity through this channel.
I always aim to think outside the box and create unique ideas. I try not to make a lot of what's already out there, and deliver something exclusive. I love whimsical, natural, rustic, vintage, shabby chic styles, but I always mix things up around here for my subscribers. 
I create seasonal & holiday DIY crafts for your home, to gift, or to make and sell.
Here are a few of my favourite things I like to create & share ~ terrariums, plant based projects, fairy gardens, Miniature scenes beautifully set up in cloches & teacups, dioramas, handmade gifts, Thrift makeovers, Trash to treasure, home decor, Dollar tree & Poundland DIYS , mixed media art & more! 
I also enjoy teaching you new techniques, hacks, tips, tricks and my very own crafty secrets. Well, enough said, I hope you come along, get inspired & have fun!

I have two other channels, both linked above on my banner.

snippet.title: HORST DIY
snippet.description:
Wir sind HORST. Unser Ziel ist es Deutschlands führende Do-It-Yourself-Community zu werden. Dafür begeistern wir immer mehr Menschen fürs Selbermachen und die Freude am Selbstgeschaffenen zu teilen.

In uns steckt die Kompetenz eines Baumarkts gepaart mit der Strahlkraft eines Social Media Influencers. Unsere Inhalte inspirieren die DIY-Szene im deutschsprachigen Raum. Wir liefern frische Ideen, inspirative Bilder & Videos und How-tos, mit denen sich jeder selbst ein schönes Zuhause machen kann.

So bringen wir der jungen und junggebliebenen Zielgruppe DIY näher und schaffen Raum, um Marken authentisch in Szene zu setzen.

snippet.title: Lovin' Life's Journey DIY
snippet.description: Hi Friends!  My name is Chantel and I love to share lots of DIY ideas here on my channel.  I don't think crafting should be expensive so most of my projects are very budget friendly!  It is my hope that I will inspire you to just step out and create.  After all, I believe that the more you create, the more creative you become!  My goal is that as I share these things with you, they will, in some way add value to your life, whether it be by teaching you something to make your life easier, sharing something to brighten your day, or showing you how to (or how not to) do something new. Whatever it may be, this is a place to celebrate and appreciate ALL of the paths that this journey called life takes us on and to learn to love life's journey together!

snippet.title: The DIY HVAC Guy
snippet.description:
⬇︎ ⬇︎ ⬇︎  Americas #1 Source For Quality, Affordable HVAC Equipment

 My name is Dave and I am an HVAC Contractor in the beautiful state of Utah. My main goal for this channel is to help viewers like yourself to gain more knowledge and be able to do repairs on your HVAC system yourself and save hundreds if not THOUSANDS of dollars!  I had to learn alot of this the hard way, so hopefully these how to videos will help you whether you are someone looking to get into this trade or if you are a DIYer!

If you are needing help with hvac repairs, sizing, replacement, and information on warranty, check out our membership over at patreon.com/diyhvacguy where you will get one on one assistance and quick response times with any questions or remote assistance! The membership is a small fee of $400/mo (cancellable at any time) and can be used as needed. 

All my favorite hvac tools can be found here:
https://www.amazon.com/shop/thediyhvacguy?ref=ac_inf_tb_vh

snippet.title: Mr and Mrs DIY
snippet.description:
We’re Craig and Laura Phillips – and here’s a huge hello from us. We’re the Mr and Mrs with a love for all things DIY (of course!)

With years of DIY experience, we decided to share our dedication to drilling, hammering, painting, fixing and creating with the country. Because we’re passionate about helping people of all ages turn a house into a home. And so, Mr & Mrs DIY was born.

From building confidence in the basics to DIY hacks and helping your money go further, we’re here to teach you (or your other half) how to finally get DIY done – the right way.

Forget basic how-to videos and dull instructions, we deliver hands-on, personal experiences from our home workshop that grow your DIY skills and are a fun day out, too!

So, turn down the tradesman, stick with us and start transforming your own home.

snippet.title: Green Cottage DIY
snippet.description:
Néhány évvel ezelőtt, saját erőből nekiálltunk egy régi ház vendégházzá való átalakításának. Mindent a lehetőségek szerint a legszebben és legkreatívabban próbáltunk megvalósítani, így jöttek a ötletek és megoldások. A vendégház mára üzemel és sok vendégünk érdeklődve hallgatta történeteinket az átalakításról. Az érdeklődés csak fokozódott, amikor kiderült néhány dologról, hogy mi is volt az valójában. Így lett eldobható raklapból asztal, emeletes ágyból kanapé, egy kupac vasból pedig kerti filagória.
Gondoltunk egyet és úgy döntöttünk, hogy ezt másoknak is meg kell mutatnunk. Illetve szeretnénk átadni azt, hogy a saját kezünkkel és sok kreativitással bármit meg lehet alkotni. Van még jó néhány ötletünk, amit meg szeretnénk valósítani; egy részét a leendő vendégeink örömére, a másik részét pedig azért, hogy ezt otthon te is meg tudd csinálni! Ígérjük, nem lesz költséges és bonyolult sem, gondolkodjunk együtt a tervezéstől a megvalósításig, és a szomszédodnak, barátaidnak, ismerőseidne

snippet.title: Chic DIY
snippet.description:
Hola Chic Lover! 👋🏻 

Soy Marian Fernández y te doy la bienvenida a Chic DIY, un canal de tutoriales de crochet o ganchillo explicados paso a paso en español  para personas diestras y zurdas. De vez en cuando grabo ratitos de charla tejeril o podcasts de tejido, donde te comparto lo que aprendo, mis diseños y lo que tejo. 

Subo contenido cuando puedo por motivos de salud, así que si realmente no te quieres perder nada, suscríbete y activa la campanita para no perderte nada.
 
Ya está disponible la opción de miembros en el canal, échale un vistazo por si te interesa, para mi sería de gran apoyo tu membresía para continuar con el canal. También puedes ayudarme de forma gratuita, ya sabes...suscríbete, comenta cada video, dale amor 💙 y comparte con quien creas que le puede gustar.
Gracias por tu apoyo y gracias por estar ahí!

Un abrazo enorme 💙

履歴
手作り歴　60年

手作りはほぼ独学で ジャンルを問わず広く浅く楽しむ
社交ダンスやオペラの舞台衣装等の製作会社を設立

物作りには  ルールが無い  身近の物の利用  リサイクル  簡単に  をモットーにしています
高価な材料を使用した作品は避けています
道具類も身近で手に入りやすい物や手作りの道具を使用

家庭用ミシンで対応可能な縫い方をしています
 
I have kept handmade dresses,bags,accessories,patchworks,art flowers, beads,crochet, and so on for 55years
"Easy and convenient recycling " is my motto.  I'd like to recommend the pleasure of handmade things.

snippet.title: Nicki's Homemade Crafts
snippet.description:
Hi, my name is Nicki, and I am the creator of Nicki's Homemade Crafts (www.nickishomemadecrafts.com). I love teaching beginners, intermediate or more advanced crocheter how to crochet and learn new crochet stitches or crochet patterns. All my patterns are free crochet patterns available on my website. Most of my patterns and tutorials come with video tutorials that are listed here on my channel. 
I'm also the creator of The Crochet Club (https://www.nickishomemadecrafts.com/crochet/the-crochet-club/) and have published over 18 Crochet Ebooks here: https://www.nickishomemadecrafts.com/crochet/crochet-ebooks/ 
I also have my own store called Nicki's Craft Store (www.nickiscraftstore.com) where you can buy merch and apparel with Crochet and Yarn memes displayed on them.
Be sure to subscribe to never miss a new video, tutorial or pattern and transform you crochet life with me and live a happier crochet life.
To get notified of new videos, make sure to click the bell next to "Subscribe" :-)

snippet.title: Eva-Konfetti DIY
snippet.description:
Всех приветствую на канале «Eva-Konfetti DIY»! Меня зовут Ева, рада знакомству! Здесь вы найдете много интересных, легких в воплощении идей для дома, дачи, квартиры и сада. 

Что-то мастерить своими руками — это мое хобби, и мне хочется поделиться своими идеями с вами, что я и делаю в рамках своего канала. К слову, у меня также есть сайт k-onfetti.ru, на котором тоже представлено много всего интересного — мастер-классы, diy, идеи рукоделия, поделки, открытки и многое другое!

snippet.title: BeatTheBush DIY
snippet.description:
Don't beat around the bush, beat the bush!
BeatTheBush enjoys good discussion but likes getting to the point even more.

The BTB DIY channel currently features even more of Francis' (aka BeatTheBush's) unique blend of efficiency, frugality, and eccentricity, as he demands both technical and financial efficiency in everything from electrical devices to almonds.  Alongside DIY videos, you'll find product tests and  reviews of the uncommon kind...

snippet.title: Walabot DIY
snippet.description:
The Walabot Multifunction Stud Finder & Wall Scanner uses Radio Frequency (RF) technology for advanced detection and In-Wall Imaging.

The tool is a cutting edge device which is paired with an Android or iOS phone to produce a visual image of what is inside drywall up to 4 inches (10 cm) deep.

The Walabot detects metal objects, wood studs, wires, pipes and can show movement behind walls, for example, rodent exploratory movements. 

Walabot DIY can be used by contractors, electricians, plumbers and DIYers in need of advanced wall imaging capabilities.

snippet.title: HOMEMADE MADNESS
snippet.description:
Hello everyone! my name is Jornt, im 23 years old and i live in The Netherlands. As you  can see my passion is to build all kinds of crazy stuff, and making videos about it. I like to do original projects, and challenge myself to always build as much of it as possible at home, and using almost no pre-made parts, real DIY.

I aim to upload at least one original, action-packed video a month, and trying keeping the video's centered around the projects and engineering, and not so much about me. (i'm not really a good vlogger)

All the stuff i do, i learnt myself. wich means everything doesn't always go perfect first try, but i will always try to find a way to make it work.

Subscribe to find out what crazy project is up next!

snippet.title: Appalachian DIY
snippet.description:
Here at Appalachian DIY we're all about doing things from scratch and getting hands-on with projects. Follow along as I lead you through simple to understand videos and tutorials to make some amazing projects that you can use every day. 
 
I'm a homeowner, so many of the projects that you will see here are improvements that I've tackled with my own home. I'm a firm believer that you can do anything as close-to, if not better than, store bought...and CHEAPER! 
 
I have Tons of hobbies and I like to make my own gear that is custom fitted to what I need. This is were my pasion for DIY-ing started. Some of my hobbies include (but not limited to), SCUBA diving, Metal lathe work, Welding, Forge/ metal casting, Four-wheeling, Running, Motorcycle riding, Photography, and Videography.
 
Occasionally you will see DIY projects related to some of these hobbies.

snippet.description:
𝓗𝓮𝓵𝓵𝓸! My name is Tata. 😘 
Welcome to my DIY channel!
I never use difficult or incomprehensible patterns in my sewing tutorials. I find some woman bags, backpacks and wallets in internet and ask to myself HOW could I 𝐦𝐚𝐤𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐬𝐤𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐟𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐚𝐥 𝐬𝐞𝐚𝐦𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬? So I take a fabric cut and sew.✂️ And it always works good!😍 That is why I'm here. I want to share my ideas with those who doesn't have professional skills of sewing but wants to have trendy clothes and bags.

👜 𝕆𝕟𝕝𝕪 𝕟𝕖𝕨 𝕠𝕨𝕟 𝔻𝕀𝕐 ℂ𝕣𝕒𝕗𝕥𝕤 𝕀𝕕𝕖𝕒𝕤: DIY Bags, Wallets, Purse & Backpacks tutorials, Home DIY Crafts, Clothes Recycle Tutorials, DIY organization Ideas, School DIYs and other. Watching my new videos every 3 days. Here you will find really interesting and useful DIY Ideas you had never seen before.

Xin chào! Mình tên là Ami, niềm đam mê của mình là búp bê và đồ vật thu nhỏ. Kênh của mình làm ra những sản phẩm đồ chơi handmade , đồ thu nhỏ, tái tạo lại vẻ đẹp cho búp bê. Những món đồ chơi mua sẵn hiện nay rất phong phú, giá cả đắt đỏ mà lại không mấy an toàn, việc tự tay làm ra những đồ chơi này giúp phát triển trí tuệ, sự sáng tạo và rèn luyện sự khéo léo. Hy vọng kênh sẽ được các bạn ủng hộ.
Kênh này dành cho lứa tuổi từ 13 trở lên và KHÔNG DÀNH CHO TRẺ EM. Búp bê mà mình sử dụng trong video này không nhằm mục đích "CHƠI" mà có sử dụng nhiều dụng cụ nguy hiểm đến trẻ nhỏ để tái tạo, làm đẹp và trang trí lại búp bê nên không phù hợp với trẻ em. Nếu bạn yêu thích búp bê và trên 13 tuổi thì kênh này phù hợp với bạn. Mãi iuuu ^^

snippet.title: DIYぷるごんチャンネル
snippet.description:
＝＝自己紹介＝＝
節約大好きDIY主婦ぷるです。
中古住宅をセルフリノベーションして再生する様子をアップしていきます。
セルフリノベーション後のお家は原則的には賃貸しています。
自分たちが住みたい家、自信を持ってお貸しできる家に仕上げることを目標としています。
実際にそこで生活しながらリフォームすることで、より快適に生活して頂けるお家を供給出来ればと思っています。
投資用で購入しても自分たちで住んじゃうなんてこともあります^^*

DIYうまくいかないことも多いです。
難しいこと複雑なこともできません。
これからたくさんチャレンジしていこうと思います。

情報源は主にインターネットですが、
「あんな事したいな～。」
「この材料はここに使えるかな？」
と調べても、情報が無かったり
良く分からなかったりする事がたくさんあります。
うまくいった事や失敗も誰かの何かの参考になればうれしいです。
材料はネットで購入する事が多いのですが、
サンプルだけでは質感など分かりづらい事も多いです。
実際に施工したらどんな感じになるか、
見てくださる人の参考になれば良いなと思い
使用した商品をなるべく記入するようにしています。

過去やったリフォーム
和式トイレを洋式トイレに
砂壁に壁紙を貼る
タイルの上に壁紙を貼る
屋根裏に断熱材
フロアタイルを張る
ブロック塀を解体
浴槽を塗装
お風呂のリフォーム
換気扇の新規設置
洗濯機置き場を新たに作る
洗面化粧台設置
混合水栓の取付け
和室を洋室に
などなど

snippet.title: The DIY Mommy
snippet.description:
Want to create a beautiful, cozy home with limited time, money and space? I'm here to help! I'm Christina Dennis AKA The DIY Mommy and I'm a DIY & decor expert sharing budget friendly ideas to help YOU build a home and life you love. From simple home organizing tips to affordable room transformations, I hope you feel inspired to tackle your next project after you watch my videos. You are capable, you are creative, and you CAN DIY the home of your dreams no matter your budget, your skill level or your schedule. Let's get started! ❤️

Our first home was an 880 square foot garage conversion, and we built our current home ourselves on a very tight budget. Through these experiences, I've learned how to decorate and organize small, budget-friendly spaces to make them both beautiful and functional. I'm sharing ALL my DIY & decor tips with you so that you can do the same!

New videos WEEKLY on SATURDAY MORNINGS with BONUS videos every month!

Thanks for stopping by.
